---
// Sin imports de React ni Lucide
---

<footer class="bg-[hsl(205_65%_35%)] text-white py-12">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <!-- Heart Icon -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6 text-[hsl(145_60%_45%)]">
            <path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.29 1.51 4.04 3 5.5l7 7Z"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="font-bold text-xl">Enfermería a Domicilio</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          Cuidado profesional sin intermediarios en Bucaramanga y su área metropolitana.
          Proyecto sin ánimo de lucro enfocado en el bienestar humano.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Contacto -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-4">Contacto</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80">
            <!-- Phone Icon -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0">
              <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>+57 300 123 4567</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80">
            <!-- Mail Icon -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0">
              <rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/>
            </svg>
            <span>contacto@enfermeria-bucaramanga.com</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-white/80">
            <!-- MapPin Icon -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <path d="M20 10c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8s-8 3.58-8 8c0 2.5 1.25 4.75 3.25 6.25L12 22l4.75-7.75C18.75 12.75 20 10.5 20 10z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Bucaramanga, Floridablanca, Girón, Piedecuesta</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Servicios -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-4">Servicios</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/80">
          <li>Cuidados posoperatorios</li>
          <li>Curaciones complejas</li>
          <li>Administración de medicamentos</li>
          <li>Atención a adultos mayores</li>
          <li>Cuidados paliativos</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Divider y créditos -->
    <div class="border-t border-white/20 pt-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
        <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">
          © 2024 Enfermería a Domicilio Bucaramanga. Proyecto sin ánimo de lucro.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/70 text-sm">
          <!-- Shield Icon -->
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Profesionales certificados por el Ministerio de Salud</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>